# CODEOWNERS - Code Ownership and Automatic Review Assignment
#
# This file defines code ownership for the OpenShift Coordination Engine.
# When a pull request modifies files in these paths, the specified owners
# are automatically assigned as reviewers.
#
# Syntax: /path/to/files @username1 @username2
#
# Documentation: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Note: As collaborators join the project, add them to relevant sections
# based on their areas of expertise.

# ==============================================================================
# Default Owner
# ==============================================================================
# Applies to all files unless a more specific rule matches below
*       @tosin2013

# ==============================================================================
# Core Code Areas
# ==============================================================================

